divs: Sighting DetailsI was on break outside my work. It was a beautiful day so I was looking upward. I had noticed a white looking spot that was hanging around a cloud. I asked the others if they knew what that was. About 6 of us saw it. It was ascending coming toward us. Then all of a sudden... it just stopped. I said look! It stopped. It stayed in 1 place for about 15 seconds. It quickly started going the other way away from us. We saw about two of them at the same time. I told the rest of the crew I wish I had gone to get the camera I keep in my desk. After break... that is just what I did. I went outside thinking I might see something and take a pic of it. I was about tired and I was just about to come in the warehouse, when towards the Memphis Airport I saw 2 black dots. I automatically thought maybe they are having a show this weekend. Hardly... what I saw next... I can't explain. They 2 dots were flying zig zagging in and out with each other... going around each other. I told myself they arn't planes because they are too close and planes don't do that. I don't blame you for what I am about to say... but these to things became as 1 and shot off. I was able to take pics of them after becoming one. After, downloading the photos, I had noticed that I caught 2 UFO's. At least I have proof of what I saw. The pictures are good but far away. If you blow them up... you can see IT AINT NO AIRCRAFT. Well... that's about it. Thanks.6
